cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM. 

The paper proposes a method to improve image clustering using text features, which suggests it could belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) or Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of topic modeling via non-negative matrix factorization suggests it could also belong to the Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the use of a common dictionary or "wisdom of the crowds" suggests it could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
